OL,5,G0200 Secret Nazi Bases
OL,6,     FLurking in the Shadows: Germany's
OL,7,     Fpreparations for WW2 began years
OL,8,     Fbefore 1939. Under various guises,
OL,9,     FGermany began work on what would
OL,10,     Fbecome their most technologically
OL,11,     Fadvanced front.
OL,12,G0300 Secret Nazi Bases
OL,13,     FHitler's Secret Underground City:
OL,14,     FIn Poland lies a forgotten Nazi
OL,15,     Fcomplex which could have sheltered
OL,16,     Fup to 27,244 people from Allied
OL,17,     Fbombs, the purpose of which
OL,18,     Flargely remains a mystery.
